# Docs Site Module

Switch the documentation experience to [Fumadocs](https://fumadocs.com/) by setting `docs_site=fumadocs`
during render. The generator provisions `docs/fumadocs.config.ts` and reserves space for MDX content.

## Validation Commands

```bash
pnpm --filter docs-fumadocs install
pnpm --filter docs-fumadocs build
```

Add navigation entries to `fumadocs.config.ts` and commit generated assets to ensure deterministic docs
builds.
